      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but \"small steps\" feel like rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. it’s just exhausting to keep fighting for a future that isn't even coming. sometimes i feel like the only logical way to deal with the dread is to just... not be a part of it anymore. does that sound crazy?",
